SQL> SET SERVEROUTPUT ON;
SQL> CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER UP
  2  BEFORE UPDATE ON DOCTOR1
  3  FOR EACH ROW
  4  BEGIN
  5  IF :OLD.SPCL!='PEDIATRIC'
  6  THEN
  7  raise_application_error(-20961,'Updation not Possible');
  8  END IF;
  9  END;
 10  /

Trigger created.

